premise_source_doc_sentence: `` Back It Up '' marks as the eighth collaboration of Lopez and Pitbull , in lined with `` Fresh Out the Oven '' in 2009 , `` On the Floor '' in 2011 , `` Dance Again '' in 2012 , `` Live It Up '' in 2013 , `` We Are One  (  Ole Ola  )  '' in 2014 with Claudia Leitte , `` Booty '' in 2014 and a song entitled `` Drinks For You  (  Ladies Anthem  )  '' from Pitbull 's Global Warming album in 2012 .
